{"tid":2439754,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英媒評選亞洲歷史球星：車范根居首","createTime":"2021-03-09T12:49:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T14:13:47.000Z","uid":29969,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d5cb06c515ba0a10f4f43e4933a4e3cebeaff860","tid":2439754,"uid":29969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T12:49:58.000Z","msg":"近日英國媒體《90分鐘》評選了歷史上的亞洲球星<br />\n<br />\n其中，韓國球星車范根位居榜首。而在前十名中，韓國球員佔據五名，日本球員佔據四名。<br />\n<br />\n第二名為菲律賓球星阿爾坎特拉，他曾效力於西班牙豪門巴塞隆拿。而孫興民和朴智星分列第三和第四。<br />\n<br />\n而第五到第十名球員分別為本田圭佑、中田英壽、金鑄成、洪明甫、中村俊輔和香川真司。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6QRV55X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6QRV55X.jpg&h=fe42a248&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ff10f51d4d42e20b37a6123698af8d11717766b","tid":2439754,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T12:50:46.000Z","msg":"玻璃心碎了，連賓仔都比唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063556d3743a32f08cd4a2eb7f59978fbb93e96c","tid":2439754,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T12:50:49.000Z","msg":"唔係拓柒第一，failed"},{"pid":"d998b4bacda5826ab6548d49c7c22b7274a62157","tid":2439754,"uid":29969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ff10f51d4d42e20b37a6123698af8d11717766b","tid":2439754,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T12:50:46.000Z","msg":"玻璃心碎了，連賓仔都比唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T12:53:12.000Z","msg":"李惠堂喺邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi